    {
      "id": "PopularPost277990",
      "post_content": "Really good card, but I think some people are confused on how it works.  \n  \nSomeone mentioned copying a counter to counter itself. No. That doesn't work. If wild richochet's on top of the stack, it is played. After that, it's already resolved. You can't make it counter itself. You'd have to choose other targets for that. For example, keep the original target of the counterspell, then make the other counterspell counter the first one. Still works, just not like you're thinking.  \n  \nAlways fun with really rigged instants or sorceries. [Hymn to Tourach](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach)? Hey, noob, discard four cards!   \n  \nAt worst, a mildly amusing way to get card advantage. At best, this wins you the game with style. ",
      "posted_by": "TwentyFifthBaam",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost277990\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Really good card, but I think some people are confused on how it works.<br/><br/>Someone mentioned copying a counter to counter itself. No. That doesn't work. If wild richochet's on top of the stack, it is played. After that, it's already resolved. You can't make it counter itself. You'd have to choose other targets for that. For example, keep the original target of the counterspell, then make the other counterspell counter the first one. Still works, just not like you're thinking.<br/><br/>Always fun with really rigged instants or sorceries. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Tourach\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach\">Hymn to Tourach</a>? Hey, noob, discard four cards! <br/><br/>At worst, a mildly amusing way to get card advantage. At best, this wins you the game with style. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '277990'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy88148\">TwentyFifthBaam</span>\r\n                                (10/24/2012 1:16:45 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n         